events.title: Avatar Meher Baba's 130th Birthday Celebration
events.desc:
Avatar Meher Baba was born on 25th February 1894 in Pune, Maharashtra. AMB Lucknow Centre celebrated Meher Baba's 130th birthday as per the following schedule -
Session 1 - 10 PM on 24th February 2024 to 5 AM on 25th February 2024
Session 2 - 5 PM to 8 PM on 25th February 2024

events.title: Meher Prem Sammelan - May 2024
events.desc: Avatar Meher Baba Lucknow Centre will celebrate Meher Prem Sammelan to commemorate Beloved Baba's visit to Lucknow on 16th May, 1946.

events.title: Meher Prem Sammelan - October 2024 (100 Years of Meher Baba's First Visit To Lucknow)
events.desc: Avatar Meher Baba Lucknow Centre will celebrate Meher Prem Sammelan, honoring Beloved Baba's visit to Lucknow in 1943 and commemorating the 31st anniversary of the establishment of the Avatar Meher Baba Lucknow Centre. This year also signifies the centenary of Meher Baba's first visit to Lucknow in March 1924, an occasion that will be celebrated by the AMB Lucknow Centre.
